snippet.title: Mom teaches Diana how to become a Superstar
snippet.description:
Diana wants to be a superstar, sing and perform on stage. Mom gives her the opportunity to understand that for the sake of her dream, one talent is not enough, she also needs to work hard.
Thanks for watching!
